This paper deals with multi-agent systems and task assignment, which are typical topics in the field of multi-agent systems (cs.MA). The proposed approach employs Monte-Carlo Tree Search (MCTS), which is a popular technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses the efficiency and effectiveness of the proposed algorithm, which are important topics in control systems (cs.SY) and machine learning (cs.LG).
